GSD.description:
clk: tegra: Fix refcount leak in tegra114_clock_init

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v5.10.150 by commit c01bfd23cc13a420b3f6a36bcab98410f49d480d, it was introduced in version v3.10 by commit 2cb5efefd6f7d3e7df9a7430b910a80515821256. For more details please see the references link.
